    "costs": null,
    "actions_taken": [],
    "summary": "Two crew members were inside a work basket using power tongs to trip in drill pipe. While attempting to stab a joint of 3 inch drill pipe into the stump, the Tong Operator swung the tongs to make up the connection. The Injured Person, assisting with the connection, noticed the tong door was closed and grabbed it to open it. The IP misjudged the tong's movement and placed his hand on the tong door as the tongs struck the drill pipe, pinching his right thumb between the tong door and the pipe joint.",
